data.description: A truly remarkable home in the heart of Historic Steilacoom! With views of the Puget Sounds, mountains, the ferry to Anderson Island, & charming downtown, you'll love the comfortable & modern living this home has to offer. Open concept floor plan downstairs, connecting the kitchen and living spaces together with light & bright windows with views of the Sound. French doors off kitchen leads to a tree deck, perfect for outdoor entertaining. Upstairs you'll find all bedrooms, with the primary bedroom having its own ensuite 5 piece bath, 2 separate closet spaces, and your very own private rooftop patio space! Bonus room has own kitchen & bathroom with separate entrance, perfect for MIL.  Spacious driveway and big attached 2 car garage!
